  Orchestration Mode
  Choose how Codex should use subagents for future turns.

  1. Full               Use explorer and worker agents for separable complex
                        work.
  2. Explore            Prefer explorer agents for broad discovery.
  3. Work               Prefer worker agents for disjoint implementation
                        scopes.
› 4. Disable (current)  Do not add orchestration guidance.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
